title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export the data in the table containing a highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data in the table should be successfully exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Locate the table containing the highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Verify that the data is exported successfully without any exceptions occurring.
